Attributes.description: Nursing practice to integrate and consolidate professional nursing knowledge, skills, and competencies in care of adults/older adults with stable/expected health care challenges and their families. Practice learning may occur in settings like community, home, inpatient, clinics and/or simulated learning.
Attributes.coreq: Co-reqs: All of NURS 300, NURS 310, NURS 321, NURS 330, NURS 352.
Attributes.date_buildings: Term: 1, Days: Mon, Start Time: 11:00, End Time: 12:00
